bantam.cfg

Class StdParamInst

  • java.lang.Object
    • bantam.cfg.TACInst
      • bantam.cfg.ParamInst
        • bantam.cfg.StdParamInst

  • public class StdParamInst
extends ParamInst
    A class representing a three-address code parameter instruction (StdParamInst). A standardf parameter instruction consists of a source value representing the actual parameter expression (inherited from ParamInst). From TACInst it also inherits an opcode (STDPARAM).
    Author:
    Marc Corliss and Lori Pietraszek
